{"tid":884979,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國會通過資助藏人1700萬美元","createTime":"2018-11-01T04:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T05:26:39.000Z","uid":47714,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"695c37f64c4b825be4bbeff83d2ee6761c97d01b","tid":884979,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:27:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/美國會通過資助藏人1700萬美元-221114945.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E8%97%8F%E4%BA%BA1700%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-221114945.html&d=uXNkVBNXjWnhZA1iHhmX7R4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=686905de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/美國會通過資助藏人1700萬美元-221114945.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國會日前通過一項開支法案，在二○一八財政年度專門向藏人社區撥款一千七百萬美元，包括西藏境內的藏人和流亡印度的藏人等。報道稱，這項法案包括用於西藏境內藏人的八百萬美元，在印度和尼泊爾藏人社區的六百萬美元，另外還有三百萬美元用於加強藏人機構和「流亡政府」的能力。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，美國這一所謂的「撥款援助」由來已久。在二○○二年，時任美國總統喬治布殊簽署了有關資助「流亡藏人」的法案後，就一直延續至今。該法案中聲稱「支持西藏人民保護其身分獨立性」，還資助了一系列藏語電台和在南亞的「流亡藏人」。"},{"pid":"af50eeb1d9091a38c28550a49baf8cee65338685","tid":884979,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd2d9c7d96eb779dc264d3f6d6e1b70c6cf0ea4","tid":884979,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be51e54050f2a3262a65a2ff5dd6a242998d89d1","tid":884979,"uid":92383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"幾時資助港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1942328c4087558e05cf06aa867a5e47d5045c55","tid":884979,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:26:39.000Z","msg":"支那夠唔夠膽收歸國有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=